      Defunct is an indie adventure game with a focus on flow,  speed and
      an engaging world. You are a broken robot that  accidentally  falls
      out of a giant cargo ship onto a post-human Earth, now inhabited by
      robots. You have to get back to your ship before its too  late! You
      are  equipped with  a Gravitize  engine. It  is used  to  create  a
      separate gravity around yourself; this is the main source  of  your
      speed.

      For more info go to : http://store.steampowered.com/app/359350/
